<h1 class="text-center">RULES:</h1>

<h2 class="offset-1 col-10">HOW TO WIN:</h2>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Spell words and bet well!  Whoever has the most money at the end of the game wins!
</p>

<h2 class="offset-1 col-10">SETUP:</h2>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Each player begins with 10&#162; and a hand of 3 Letters.  Depending on the number of players, the bank will begin with
    50&#162; (2-players), 60&#162; (3-players), or 80&#162; (4-players).  Click on the 'X' next to a player to remove them,
    and the buttons below to add new players.  You can also toggle if a player is human or computer controlled.  Click 'Start Game' when you are ready 
    to begin!
</p>

<br>
<h2 class="offset-1 col-10">Playing A Round:</h2>

<h3 class="offset-1 col-10">Setting Aside Cards for Spelling:</h3>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">At the start of a round of play, one player must choose any number of cards from their
    hand (including 0) to use in spelling a word.  At the end of the round, they will use these letters and the
    letters in the middle (known as the Research Line) to spell a word.  The cards set aside from the hand MUST 
    be used to spell the word.  Click on a card in your hand to select it, then click 'Confirm' to submit your
    selection.
</p>
