<br>
<h3 class="offset-1 col-10">Betting:</h3>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">After the spelling player as set aside cards from their hand (if any), all of the other
    players must bet on which letters from the Research Line will be used.  To place a bet, click on a card from the
    Research Line (the top row of cards).  You may place as many bets as you like, on any number of cards.  You must
    place at least 1&#162; in bets.  You cannot place bets if you run out of money, or large bets on certain cards
    (see Card Rules below).  The amount that you have bet will show up on the bottom of the card.  Click 'Confirm'
    when you are happy with your bets, or 'Cancel' if you want to undo and make changes.
</p>
