</div>

<br>
<br>
<h3 class="offset-1 col-10">Spelling:</h3>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Once all other players have made their bets, the spelling player attempts to spell a word.
    If they cannot (or simply choose not to), they may click 'Skip Turn'.  They will be dealt a new hand of 3 cards,
    but lose their turn.  All bets will be refunded.
</p>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Normally, however, a player will choose to spell a word.  Click
    on the Letters you wish to use in the order that the word will be spelled.  You can click on the Letters a second
    time to return them to their origional spot.  Once you have spelled a word, click 'Confirm'.
</p>
<div class="col-10 offset-1">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
