    </div>
</div>
<br>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Players will notice stacks of money on the Research Line Letters (the middle row). Stacks
    of money in the CENTER of the card represents that Letter's Ledger.  This is money that the speller will collect
    if they use that Letter.  Stacks of money on the EDGES of the card represent other player's bets.  This is how
    much the speller will have to pay to use that Letter.
</p>
<div class="col-10 offset-1">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/djcc248bk/image/upload/w_400/v1625521092/ExtraExtra/Characters/Spelling2_tdpvax.png" alt="">
