        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Click 'Pay and End' to pay those who bet on Letters that were used in the word and end 
    the round.  Any unused bets will be moved into their Letter's Ledger.  The speller draws back up to a hand of 3,
    and the Research Line is refilled to 5 (or 6, see Card Rules below).  The next player becomes the new speller and
    a new round begins.
</p>


<br>
<br>
<h2 class="offset-1 col-10">End of the Game:</h2>
<p class="offset-1 col-10">Play continues until the Bank runs out of money.  At this point, everyone except the starting
    player gets one more round to be the spelling player.  After that, whoever has the most money is the winner!  If players
    have an equal amount of money, they share the victory.
</p>

